The ability to use the Alt-H, Alt-B etc... key shortcuts on the web interface to jump to different parts of the application is a great feature.  I'd like to see these type of shortcuts expanded to more options on each interface.  I.e., instead of just the main navigation options having shortcut key bindings, add them to most links on each interface.  Being able to navigate a web interface without using the mouse would be incredible.

-- Ryan Daigle

