At the same time we should consolidate all icons for popups.

It would be nice to be able to plug in a class to do custom validation of username/password. Something like 

public class MyLoginValidator implements JiraLoginValidator{

     public boolean isValid(String username, String password){
          // go off and do complicated lookup in enterprise 
          //  directory service
           return doComplicatedEnterpriseDirectoryLookup(username, password)

     }
}

