For releases, I want to call filters from an external script (in this case: apache ant). When in private mode, this gives you an information page about filters.

URL: http://myserver/jira/secure/IssueNavigator.jspa?requestId=10031&decorator=printable&tempMax=1000

I like the option to call a page, optionally referencing a named filter, specifying the user & password as arguments, outputting a nice HTML page containing 'resolved issues' and 'known issues' for a certain release.

